      "content": "thanks. i'm worried though, if the melatonin makes it even stronger, is there like a specific amount of melatonin i should take with the ambien to reach that sweet spot for deep sleep? like would 5mg or 10mg be better to pair with the pill? i just want to make sure i don't underdo it and end up staring at the ceiling again.",
